title: Finally an iPhone bumper that is sexy and protects.
text:
Tuesday, September 8, 2015 OREM, UTAH: ThanoTech Inc. â€“ manufacturer of the K11 Bumper for the iPhone 6, 6s, 6 Plus and 6s Plus is releasing their Kickstarter campaign. Due to the press release of the iPhone 6s and 6s Plus on September 9PthP we have prepared for the high demand that is possible. This also gives great writing material pre and post announcement.
ThanoTech is seeking $50,000 via Kickstarter to fund the K11 Bumper. Funding begins September 3, 2015 at 8am PST/11am EST and ends on October 1, 2015 at 11am PST. Upon successful funding, ThanoTech plans to ship the K11 Bumper in November, 2015. Having been in the phone and accessories industry for almost 10 years, we are confident on the fulfillment date.
Highlights:
High quality materials are verified in a drop test at 6 feet (2 meters) with no damage to either product
Flexible TPU provides ease when removing and installing
Mirroring colors to the iPhone with Space Grey TPU/Space Grey, White TPU/Silver, and White TPU/Gold. Kickstarter special Black TPU/Space Grey and Black TPU/Black
The campaign has a limited reward of 50 fully custom color bumpers
Compatible with 3PrdP party chargers and headphones
Raised protection for the rear camera
Kickstarter campaign from August 25 to September 28, 2015
Pricing and Availability
MSRP of K11 Bumper is $39.95 (Kickstarter backers can get it starting at $18 individually and down to $14 in bulk)
Shipping in November, 2015 upon successful Kickstarter funding
